data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT: - Welcome to 2505 Jackson Heights Drive, an updated charming and spacious home located in the heart of Sebring, Florida. This well-maintained property features 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms. The open floor plan and ample natural light make this home perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying everyday living. The large backyard offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and relaxation. Conveniently located near downtown Sebring & Lake Jackson. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home!  Irrigation System keeps your yard looking good all year long!    Updates Include: Roof=2022, AC=2020, Updated Bathrooms=2022, New Flooring & Painting=2023,Trees Trimmed=2023, Irrigation Updated to 8 Zones = 2023
